snippet.title: Divorce With Amber Heard Could Put Johnny Depp's Estimated $400M In Jeopardy
snippet.description: Amber Heard has filed for divorce from Johnny Depp after just 15 months of marriage. The actress cited "irreconcilable differences" as she filed for divorce in Los Angeles Superior Court. Their separation date is listed as Sunday on the documents, according to reports. The couple did not have a prenup and Depp has reportedly hired a top divorce lawyer. Depp's estimated worth is $400M which could make the divorce get ugly. #InsideEdition
